            <img src="/placeholder-avatar-1.jpg" alt="Marcus Torres Avatar" class="placeholder-avatar">
            <div class="author-info">
              <strong>Marcus Torres</strong>
              <span>Adam, Youth Exchange 2024</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"I want to say BIG THANK YOU for what you are doing for us! I am so grateful for this project, it is a blessing, I am satisfied for choosing it, I am numb and I am so grateful!"</p>
