            <div class="author-info">
              <strong>Kristine L</strong>
              <span>Long-term CES Volunteer 2024</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"I loved every bit of this week. And especially all of you. I hope everyone had the same amount of fun or even more than I had. I will miss you guys like hell and I will see every one of you again"</p>
